      "text": "As co-chairs of the Caucus on Black-Jewish Relations, @RepNikema and I convened colleagues to learn more about the Rosenwald School Project.\n\nWe must continue the history of Black and Jewish Americans standing together to promote of education, social justice and civil rights. https://t.co/p1crYGxDyJ",
