      "text": "Trump guts global health programs that keep people around the world healthy. Infectious diseases don’t respect borders, and his recklessness puts America in danger.\n\nGreat to meet @RESULTS_Tweets and fight to eradicate HIV/AIDS, Tuberculosis, and Malaria alongside them. https://t.co/YYpKEoqKz7",
