      "text": "My top priority is making sure life is more affordable. Whether it’s fighting costly, illegal Trump tariffs or protecting Social Security and Medicare, Democrats stand up for our seniors.\n\nGlad to join The Pointe at Plantation to share my work for them. https://t.co/y3sg8VfUB7",
